graph TD
    A[Local Developer Laptop] -->|Writes PyTorch Script| B[train.py]
    B --> C[SageMaker SDK Estimator]
    
    subgraph AWS Cloud Ecosystem
    C -->|Spins Up| D[Managed EC2 Instance]
    D -->|Pulls Image| E[AWS Deep Learning Container]
    D -->|Downloads Data| F[S3 Bucket Data]
    E --> G[Executes train.py]
    G -->|Saves Artifact| H[S3 Bucket Model Output]
    end
    
    I[AWS IAM Role] -.->|Grants Permissions| D
    I -.->|Allows Read| F
    I -.->|Allows Write| H
